    <section class="whhs_intro">
      <h1>Meetings @ Sunday Walton Hall Hotel & Spa</h1>
      <p>Nestled in 65 acres of exquisite Warwickshire countryside, Sunday Walton Hall Hotel & Spa is a premier destination for corporate and private events. The historic 16th-century Hall, once home to the Mordaunt family, combines timeless elegance with state-of-the-art facilities, creating an inspiring setting for your meetings.</p>
      <p>Designed as a dedicated training, conference, and events venue, our contemporary hotel features purpose-built facilities ideal for board meetings, training sessions, and large-scale events. The self-contained Courtyard Suite accommodates up to 180 delegates theatre-style, perfect for product presentations and corporate gatherings.</p>
      <p>Our 25 event spaces, including meeting rooms, restaurants, and outdoor areas, offer unmatched flexibility, set against a backdrop of Victorian gardens and manicured lawns. All rooms include complimentary WiFi, with our in-house AV team ready to support your technical needs.</p>
      <h2>Hotel Facilities at a Glance</h2>
      <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <li class="whhs_facility-item"><i class="fas fa-chair"></i> 25 event spaces, including meeting rooms and restaurants, largest seating 220 theatre-style</li>
        <li class="whhs_facility-item"><i class="fas fa-bed"></i> 197 bedrooms, including 37 luxury rooms in our 16th Century Hall</li>
        <li class="whhs_facility-item"><i class="fas fa-utensils"></i> Moncreiffe Restaurant, Mordaunt Restaurant, Orangery Restaurant</li>
        <li class="whhs_facility-item"><i class="fas fa-cocktail"></i> Conservatory Bar, Lemon Tree Bar, Hall Lounge</li>
        <li class="whhs_facility-item"><i class="fas fa-spa"></i> Spa & Leisure Club with indoor pool, gym, sauna, and beauty rooms</li>
        <li class="whhs_facility-item"><i class="fas fa-lock"></i> Exclusive use available</li>
        <li class="whhs_facility-item"><i class="fas fa-wifi"></i> Complimentary WiFi throughout</li>
        <li class="whhs_facility-item"><i class="fas fa-parking"></i> Ample free on-site parking</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="whhs_packages">
      <h2>Flexible Packages</h2>
      <p>Our bespoke day and 24-hour delegate packages are tailored to your meeting needs, ensuring a seamless and productive event. Packages include:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
        <li>Complimentary standard WiFi (upgrades available)</li>
        <li>Personal greeting from your dedicated meeting host</li>
        <li>Fully set-up room with coffee or specialty teas on arrival</li>
        <li>Unlimited refreshments throughout the day, served as you prefer</li>
        <li>Optional coffee and snack to-go for delegates</li>
        <li>Seasonal, healthy lunch options tailored to your requirements</li>
        <li>LCD screens with user guides and on-site AV support</li>
        <li>Transparent ‘one bill’ account with no hidden costs</li>
      </ul>
